-- South African Treasury Names Sikhakhane as Spokesman, Business Day Reports
-- Paul Richardson
-- 2010-06-18T05:01:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/south-african-treasury-names-sikhakhane-as-spokesman-business-day-reports.html

          
          
             The South African Treasury named
Jabulani Sikhakhane, a former journalist, as its new spokesman,
Business Day reported, citing the Finance Ministry.  
          
          


  


        